Tyrael: Well Ultra Magnus was always a warrior of great strength, but
I don't believe all this Matrix talk. He was not able to summon it
when Unicron threatened Cybertron and he will not do so now.
Especially if we have him in our hands.

He left the table and went to the communication post in the next room.
